 secularist, very materialist, post-modern culture that knows who their enemy is.\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very secularist\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"very materialist, post-modern culture\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2429}, {\"ngram\": \"their enemy\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Christian churches stand as the great institutional opponents to this worldview.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999918106249152, \"rank\": 8.189442161625677e-06, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the great institutional opponents\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"this worldview\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a philosophical, cultural struggle, and they know who the enemy is, so when they have a chance, they mock the enemy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a philosophical, cultural struggle\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"the enemy\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2645}, {\"ngram\": \"the enemy\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think we should simply acquiesce,\\\" he continued.\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you go back to the Lord himself\\u2026 to turn the other cheek and so on is not a recommendation to acquiescence or to quietude.\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Lord\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"the other cheek\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"a recommendation\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a manner of engaging evil when you see it, to do it nonviolently, to be sure, but it's a way of engaging and getting\\u2026 in the face of things that we see as wicked.\\\"\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 3026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a manner\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"evil\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2955}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 2992}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SUPREME COURT DENIES DESANTIS IN LEGAL BATTLE OVER DRAG QUEEN BAN The controversial Olympics displayfeatured numerous performers, including drag queens and a large woman in a halo crown, parodying \\\"The Last Supper,\\\" a universally recognizable painting by renaissance artist Leonardo da Vinci of Christ and his apostles on the night of Passover before Christ's passion and death.\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3303, \"end\": 3320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.541151628327281e-26, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 3380, \"end\": 3386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999997509867481, \"rank\": 2.490134279954733e-07, \"text\": \"Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SUPREME COURT\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3041}, {\"ngram\": \"DESANTIS\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3057}, {\"ngram\": \"LEGAL BATTLE\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"DRAG QUEEN BAN\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3093}, {\"ngram\": \"The controversial Olympics\", \"from\": 3094, \"t